## Governance & MNPI Compliance

Financial services environments require strict data access controls. The accelerator provides complete MNPI governance out of the box.

### Architecture

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                   GOVERNANCE LAYER                            │
│                                                              │
│  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────────┐  │
│  │ Column Masks │  │  Row Filters │  │  Dynamic Views   │  │
│  │              │  │              │  │                  │  │
│  │ mask_func()  │  │ filter_func()│  │ CASE WHEN        │  │
│  │ ALTER COLUMN │  │ ALTER TABLE  │  │ is_member(group) │  │
│  │ SET MASK     │  │ SET ROW FILTR│  │ THEN real_value  │  │
│  │              │  │              │  │ ELSE masked      │  │
│  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────────┘  │
│                            │                                  │
│                            ▼                                  │
│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │
│  │              AUDIT LOG (7-year retention)              │   │
│  │  who | accessed | what | when | from_where            │   │
│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Governance in YAML Specs

```yaml
governance:
  classification: mnpi          # public | internal | confidential | mnpi
  embargo_hours: 24             # Data hidden for 24h after creation
  mnpi_columns:                 # Columns requiring protection
    - notional_amount
    - counterparty_name
    - pnl
  column_masks:                 # What unauthorized users see
    notional_amount: "0.00"
    counterparty_name: "'[RESTRICTED]'"
  row_filter: "trade_date < current_date() - INTERVAL 1 DAY"
  owner_group: risk_trading_desk  # Group with full access
```

### Generated SQL (example)

```sql
-- Column Mask Function
CREATE OR REPLACE FUNCTION production.risk_bronze.mask_notional_amount(val DECIMAL)
RETURNS DECIMAL
RETURN CASE WHEN is_account_group_member('risk_trading_desk') THEN val ELSE 0.00 END;

-- Apply Mask
ALTER TABLE production.risk_bronze.trade_events
ALTER COLUMN notional_amount SET MASK production.risk_bronze.mask_notional_amount;

-- Row Filter Function
CREATE OR REPLACE FUNCTION production.risk_bronze.filter_trade_events()
RETURNS BOOLEAN
RETURN CASE 
  WHEN is_account_group_member('risk_trading_desk') THEN TRUE
  ELSE trade_date < current_date() - INTERVAL 1 DAY
END;

-- Apply Row Filter
ALTER TABLE production.risk_bronze.trade_events
SET ROW FILTER production.risk_bronze.filter_trade_events ON ();
```

