## Wave Planning Dashboard

Track migration progress with SQL dashboard views.

```python
from aws2lakehouse.dashboard import WavePlanningDashboard

dashboard = WavePlanningDashboard(catalog="production", schema="migration_tracking")
sql = dashboard.generate_all_sql()
# Execute in SQL Warehouse to create:
#   - pipeline_inventory table
#   - wave_config table
#   - migration_progress table (daily append)
#   - v_inventory_summary (tile metrics)
#   - v_wave_progress (completion % per wave)
#   - v_risk_heatmap (domain × complexity × impact)
#   - v_effort_burndown (line chart)
#   - v_dependencies (blocked/resolved status)
```

Build a Lakeview dashboard on top of these views for real-time tracking.

